Description: Condition: This Fender Mustang 90 has been barely used, and is in excellent condition with little to no signs of wear! The Mustang 90 has a distinctive sound that will take you back to your garage-band days. This guitar thrives on nonconformity, and now features upgraded components that are great for players who march to the beat of their own drum. They are entirely flexible, stacked with MP-90 pickups in the neck and bridge with low-end punch and gnarly mid range. They also feature a 9.5" radius and a comfortable "C" shaped neck.
